title: Your place, your future – have your say (Suffolk Coastal District Council)
text: ( Source : Suffolk Coastal District Council ) Suffolk Coastal District Council is urging local people to have their say on shaping the future development of the area. The Council has now published two Preferred Options Consultation documents
